  "texts": [
    "Burnout scores were also obtained within the survey using the Maslach Burnout Inventory (MBI), specifically the Human Services Survey for",
    "TABLE 1 An overview of the areas of worklife model.",
    "Lack of fit: A chronic workload that exceeds individuals' capacity to meet their professional demands without an opportunity to recover from strenuous tasks/periods of time.",
    "Fit: A sustainable workload that provides professional opportunities to use and grow skills while providing opportunities for rest.",
    "Lack of fit: Insufficient opportunity to make decisions around the nature of one's work, including shaping the environment to meet the demands of the job."
  ]
}